Package: precisexpexa
Title: Server-Side Pexa Wrapper for the PRECISE-X Model
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Mohsen", "Sadatsafavi", email = "mohsen.sadatsafavi@ubc.ca", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"))
Description: Hosts the PRECISE-X model on the Pexa cloud modelling platform.
    Provides the entry points the Pexa executor invokes (default input,
    input validation, and model execution), translating between the Pexa
    call contract and the core PRECISE-X functions.
Depends: R (>= 3.6.0)
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
